title: VTech Baby: Lil' Critters Roll & Discover Ball
description: It’s a circus of fun with the Lil Critters Roll & Discover Ball by VTech. Your little one can toss, shake and roll this bright ball to hear cheerful music and sounds while strengthening their motor skills. Playful animal characters and soft textures will capture your child’s attention and encourage exploration. Pressing the big star button introduces numbers and animals. This soft ball has loads of entertainment for your active baby, all rolled up into one toy.
